OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FHarry Kane told ITV Sport England is
OL,8,Fpreparing to take on the legendary
OL,9,FLionel Messi and his resilient
OL,10,FArgentina side
OL,12,FHarry Kane said his team does not want
OL,13,Fto focus on the "surrounding history"
OL,14,Fbetween England and Argentina ahead of
OL,15,Ftheir World Cup semi-final showdown on
OL,16,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
