PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784081889
OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FThe upcoming match has revived one of
OL,8,Ffootball's fiercest rivalries, with
OL,9,Fthe long-running Falkland Islands
OL,10,Fdispute adding political tension to
OL,11,Fthe contest.
OL,13,FFollowing their victory over
OL,14,FSwitzerland in the quarter-finals, the
OL,15,FSouth American football team was
OL,16,Ffilmed singing an anti-England song
OL,17,Fabout defeating the Three Lions "for
OL,18,Fthe Malvinas" - the Spanish name for
OL,19,Fthe British Overseas Territory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784081889
OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FWhen asked about this on Monday, the
OL,8,FEngland captain told ITV Sport: "I
OL,9,Fthink it's not something you want to
OL,10,Ffocus too much on the surrounding the
OL,11,Fhistory, and yeah, that's all part of
OL,12,Fit, and that's what you guys will talk
OL,13,Fabout.
OL,15,F"But from players' point of view, it's
OL,16,Fus against a great team who are smart,
OL,17,Fwho are tactical, who know how to buy
OL,18,Ffouls, know how to slow the game down."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784081889
OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FKane said he was looking forward to
OL,8,Fthe fact that "two giants" are meeting
OL,9,Fin a World Cup semi-final, adding that
OL,10,F"the rest of it is just a small part
OL,11,Ffor us".
OL,13,F"In these moments, I think back to
OL,14,Fbeing a kid and having dreams and what
OL,15,Fit would be like to play in these
OL,16,Fgames," he added. "This is as big as
OL,17,Fit gets."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
