OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FPolice have stepped up security across
OL,8,FAtlanta as the city prepares to host
OL,9,Fthe game at the Mercedes-Benz Stadium
OL,10,F` a fixture fans have said has "so
OL,11,Fmuch history and so much rivalry".
