OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784081889
OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FIt will be the first World Cup
OL,8,Fknockout meeting between the nations
OL,9,Fsince David Beckham's red card in
OL,10,FEngland's dramatic last-16 exit in
OL,11,F1998. The Three Lions went on to lose
OL,12,Fthe game in penalties.
OL,14,FReigning World Cup champion Argentina
OL,15,Fis being led by Lionel Messi, who
OL,16,Fholds the record for the most trophies
OL,17,Fin football history and is currently
OL,18,Fthe top goal scorer of the 2026 World
OL,19,FCup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784081889
OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FSpeaking about the team, Kane said:
OL,8,F"What a tough team to play against,
OL,9,Fbut hopefully that brings the best out
OL,10,Fin us."
OL,12,FOn Messi, he added: "We know how good
OL,13,Fof a player he is...but the game is
OL,14,Fagainst Argentina, not Leo Messi."
OL,16,FThe Duke of Sussex told the former
OL,17,Frugby union player that he thinks the
OL,18,Fgame is "coming home" for England.
OL,20,FCredit: Joe Marler Will See You Now
OL,21,Fpodcast
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1784081889
OL,3,CHarry Kane: England not focused on
OL,4,C'surrounding history' before Argentina
OL,5,Cclash
OL,7,FThere is some royal optimism for the
OL,8,FThree Lions, too.
OL,10,FSpeaking on the Joe Marler Will See
OL,11,FYou Now podcast, Prince Harry was
OL,12,Fasked by the England rugby legend if
OL,13,Fhe could swap lives with Harry Styles,
OL,14,FHarry Kane, or Harry Potter, who would
OL,15,Fhe choose?
OL,17,F"Kane on a winning day," the Duke of
OL,18,FSussex said, adding: "I think it's
OL,19,Fcoming home."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
